<section class="section-block prose-block">
  <h2>Submit to SHIT</h2>
  <p>We welcome fictional, satirical, AI-generated, semi-serious, and useful absurdity manuscripts.</p>
  <div class="button-row">
    <a class="button-primary" href="<%= theme.github.submit_issue_url %>">Submit via GitHub Issues</a>
    <a class="button-secondary" href="<%= shit_page_path('policies') %>">Policies</a>
  </div>
  <ol class="ordered-list">
    <li>Open a GitHub Issue.</li>
    <li>Select the Manuscript Submission template.</li>
    <li>Provide the title, abstract, article type, authors, and evidence status.</li>
    <li>Wait for editorial hallucination.</li>
  </ol>
</section>
